In the past 25 years America’s stock market has soared. But with trade wars and corporates gearing up their balance sheets in the hopes that the good times will roll on for ever will the bull continue to run? To find out Edgar Mafoko, Portfolio Manager at FNB Wealth and Investments, Bruce Main, founder, Ivy Asset Management and Francois Strydom, Portfolio Manager at Momentum Securities join CNBC Africa’s Fifi Peters on this episode of Portfolio Watch....